cs.SD, cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.CL, cs.LG

The paper deals with aligning audio and video signals, which involves both speech processing and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SD (Sound), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves natural language processing, which falls under cs.CL (Computation and Language), and machine learning, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
